      <h1 class='title'>"Stakeholder" Investment Products</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 15 July 2003 vol 409 cc21-2WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_21ws' title='Col. 21WS &mdash; HC Deb 15 July 2003 vol 409 c21WS' name='column_21ws' href='#column_21ws' rel='bookmark'>21WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0409P0-02338'>
        <a name='S6CV0409P0_20030715_CWS_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-paul-boateng' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0409P0_20030715_CWS_21' title='Link to this speech by Mr Paul Boateng' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-paul-boateng" title="Mr Paul Boateng">The Chief Secretary to the Treasury (Mr. Paul Boateng)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0409P0-02338">The Treasury and the Department for Work and Pensions are today publishing a Government response to their consultation paper "Proposed Product Specifications for Sandler 'Stakeholder' Products", which was launched on 5 February. It takes forward one of the main recommendations of the Sandler review of<a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_22ws' title='Col. 22WS &mdash; HC Deb 15 July 2003 vol 409 c22WS' name='column_22ws' href='#column_22ws' rel='bookmark'>22WS</a>
          July 2002. Copies will be available in the Libraries of the House. The document is also available on the Treasury and Department for Work and Pensions websites.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
